metadata.name: ÆRRANS SAGGITÆ
metadata.description:
This limited edition piece bridges Gabriel's fine art flower photography with an anthropomorphic leaning, with the subject clearly exuding emotions of longing and desire. 

Shot by GDR in his Manhattan studio on a Leica TL2 with Sigma 30mm 1.4 in the Spring of 2022

Gabrieldeanroberts.com
